	</font>

112
00:08:18,155 --> 00:08:20,075
<font color=#00ff00>
	Direkt schön raus schneiden.
	</font>

113
00:08:20,595 --> 00:08:22,075
<font color=#00ff00>
	Wunderbar.
	</font>

114
00:08:23,315 --> 00:08:25,195
<font color=#00ff00>
	Vielen Dank.
	</font>

115
00:08:25,715 --> 00:08:26,795
<font color=#ffffff>
